  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "## Feature Request\r\n\r\n### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe:\r\nJemalloc has stats about memory allocated and deallocated by each thread. We can use this metrics to get an approximate how memory distribute.\r\n\r\nWe can maintain a global map that stores pointer of the metrics when a thread is started, and cleared before the thread exits. The key to attain the pointer is `thread.allocatedp` and `thread.deallocatedp`.\r\n\r\nAnother useful information is arena that bound to the thread. It can be obtained by `thread.arena`. The information can be stored with allocation metrics and output to response when allocation is accessed at https://github.com/tikv/tikv/blob/master/src/server/service/debug.rs#L371.\r\n",
